sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User Browser
    participant F as React Frontend
    participant A as Express API
    participant R as Replit Auth
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    U->>F: Click "Login"
    F->>R: Redirect to Replit Auth
    R->>R: User authenticates
    R->>F: Redirect with session cookie
    F->>A: API request with cookie
    A->>A: isAuthenticated middleware
    A->>A: Extract claims.sub (userId)
    A->>DB: Query user data
    DB->>A: Return data
    A->>F: JSON response
    F->>U: Render dashboard
